{"tid":186870,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"改善文言文方法","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T22:36:16.000Z","uid":30859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"819a1c89a3f5bec1ddf37989dee522d6cdbe5d89","tid":186870,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"睇多d文言文<br />\n今日推介《笑林廣記》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屄打彈<br />\n<br />\n    一尼欲心甚熾﹐以蘿蔔代陽﹐大肆抽送﹐暢所欲為。不料用力太猛﹐折其半截<br />\n在內。挖之不出﹐漸至腫脹。延醫看視﹐醫將兩手陰傍按捺﹐良久突出﹐剛打在醫<br />\n人臉上。醫者嘆曰﹕&ldquo;我也醫千醫萬﹐從未見屄打彈!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n半處子<br />\n<br />\n    有寡婦嫁人而索重聘。 媒曰﹕ &ldquo;再醮與初婚不同﹐誰肯出次高價。&rdquo;婦曰﹕<br />\n&ldquo;我還是處子﹐未曾破身。&rdquo;媒曰﹕&ldquo;眼見嫁過人﹐今做孤孀﹐那個肯信﹖&rdquo;婦曰﹕<br />\n&ldquo;實不相瞞﹐先夫陽具渺小﹐故外面半截﹐雖則重婚﹐裡邊其實是個處子。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"acdfd90a6589c3adbabd1d4494599d15c9fdff61","tid":186870,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994a77ad8d9bd25c2e0abe2c960a4d0643e8ba0c","tid":186870,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"直接讀韓非子好過"},{"pid":"e931001ae291e9afb0459de6aa8fcb3e40d99473","tid":186870,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"我都想改善，可以點做<br />\n<br />\n利：返工狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab29d41de29ca6549b52d02dba88ff6c8875dec","tid":186870,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"104c867be77edb56d0b508bfd2be2c4f35cb7a67","tid":186870,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"ching，呢種係古白話，唔係文言文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dc1ad7e959b7b7d02dbf59f85f0ba10dc23807","tid":186870,"uid":30859,"like":0,"disl